pageContext.claim: “So the job numbers were fantastic. The best numbers we've had in many years. It shocked Wall Street analysts. It didn't shock me. I know what's going on. But the job numbers were beyond anybody's expectations. Really, hundreds of thousands more than your top picks. So that was a great thing.”
pageContext.analysis: The preliminary December job numbers were strong, but to say they are the best in "many years" is an exaggeration. Monthly job numbers have been higher at least five times since 2012.
